Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_mmmc_version(25.10)                              init_mmmc_version(25.10)

Name
       init_mmmc_version

Syntax
         init_mmmc_version {1 2}

       Type: Enum,

       Default: 1

       Specifies  the  version of MMMC to use for a design. It must be set be-
       fore init_design. If you try to change it after init_design,  the  tool
       will ignore the change and give a warning.

